<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT18">
<l>kārvaṇṇan tirumēṉi kaṇṇum vāyuṅ</l>
<l>kaittalamu maṭiyiṇaiyuṅ kamala vaṇṇam</l>
<l>pārvaṇṇa maṭamaṅkai pattar pittar</l>
<l>paṉimalarmēl pāvaikkup pāvañ ceytēṉ</l>
<l>ērvaṇṇa veṉpētai yeñcol kēḷā</l>
<l>ḷemperumāṉ tiruvaraṅka meṅkē yeṉṉum</l>
<l>nīrvaṇṇaṉ nīrmalaikkē pōvē ṉeṉṉu</l>
<l>mituvaṉṟō niṟaivaḻintār niṟku māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I [must have] committed a sin against the Lady of the dewy blossom</l>
<l rend="indent">of the mad one who is [also] devoted to the simple maiden whose form is the earth,</l>
<l>[Of the one with] a body the the color of rainclouds,</l>
<l rend="indent">and lotus-colored eyes, mouth, palms, and both feet.</l>
<l>My foolish [girl] of beautiful figure doesn’t hear my words.</l>
<l rend="indent">She says, “Where is our Lord’s Tiruvaraṅkam?”</l>
<l>She says, “I’ll go to the sea-hued one’s Nīrmalai.”</l>
<l rend="indent">Isn’t this the way those whose perfection  was ruined remain?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
